  <title>Motion Dimension</title>
  <keywords>
    <keyword>Function-Block<keyword>Motion-Dimension</keyword></keyword>
  </keywords>
  <body>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Motion-Dimension FB</text> defines the Angle or Linear Distance between two Parts that are joined with a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Pin-Joint">Pin-Joint</link> or a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Slide-Joint">Slide-Joint</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">The Motion-Dimension value between the two Parts is continually updated by motion-values &apos;passed to&apos; the Motion-Dimension FB from other FBs at the input-connector with &apos;wires&apos;.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Motion-Dimension">Add Motion-Dimension FB</link>.</para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
  </body>
</topic>
